snippet.title: New Robots with laser bolt weapon and oil splatter (Indie Game UE4 - Regain Earth)
snippet.description:
We have introduced new Robot AI enemies in our last update for our Indie Game Title. Armed with a laser bolt rife and showing oil platter when getting hit. I hope you like it. Feedback and suggestions very welcome!

Subscribe this channel or join us at Twitter, Steam or Reddit to stay up to date! 
Regain Earth: First Strike is a Sci-Fi Shooter Indie-Game made by a single Indie Dev with Unreal Engine 4. 

Link to last Steam Update:
https://store.steampowered.com/newshub/app/1408710/view/2886201183513613545
